item.title: SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Network_PerformanceStorage_Iscsi
item.description: SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Network_PerformanceStorage_Iscsi Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Network_PerformanceStorage_Iscsi data type contains general information relating to a single SoftLayer billing item whose item category code is ‘performance_storage_iscsi’ Local allowCancellationFlag Flag to check if a billing item can be cancelled. 1 = yes. 0 = no. Type: integer associatedBillingItemId This is sometimes populated for orphan billing items that are not attached to servers. Billing items like secondary portable IP addresses fit into this category.
